data.description: Solid ranch home with full basement. Four bedrooms and one full bath on the main level, non-conforming bedroom in the basement with another full bath. Large family room downstairs with lots of storage. Beautiful three season porch off the back, there is air conditioning to this room. Covered front porch to the sun set. Two stall detached garage (tandem) and another single stall, detached garage along with a yard shed for lots of room to store your toys. All appliances included, city water and sewer and natural gas. Great family home with lots of bedrooms close to area parks, schools and shopping.
